		<title>Chamoun calls Rai&#8217;s statements on Syria, Hezbollah “a fatal sin&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://www.yalibnan.com/2011/10/03/chamoun-calls-rais-statements-on-syria-hezbollah-%e2%80%9ca-fatal-sin/</link>
